This is a '''list of ovens'''. An [[oven]] is a thermally insulated chamber used for the [[heating]], [[baking]] or [[drying]] of a substance,<ref>[http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/oven Oven]. Merriam-webster.com. Retrieved on 2011-11-23.</ref> and most commonly used for [[cooking]]. [[Kiln]]s and [[furnace]]s are special-purpose ovens, used in [[pottery]] and [[metalworking]], respectively.
==Ovens==
